column2: Camron Mattocks a s Dakota Mayfield run PRs at the end of a long day in the 300m Dash. 37.86 and 39.72 respectively.
Margot Laughner runs her first 300m dash ever and runs an amazing 44.53. That is the #2 freshman time all time at Reservoir.
Sophia Cinotti runs a big PR in the 300m dash! 46.02. Good job and way to be aggressive in the race.
Davina Gyiamh runs 1:27.41. New personal best time in the 500m dash!
Vincent Stevens runs a PR in the 500m dash!  1:13.32. Great work buddy!
